Get free icons in Plumpy design style

Plumpy is a consistent pack of bright graphics in a cartoonish decorative style.

They will add beauty and fun to any web page, mobile app screen, newsletter, infographic, custom popup, card, or presentation.

Download free icons in different themes in Plumpy style for your UI and graphic design needs. You can also edit the images you want right on the spot.

The free graphics are pixel-perfect to fit your design and are available in both PNG and vector.
